Name:           gnome-user-share
Version:        43.0
Release:        0
Summary:        GNOME user file sharing
License:        GPL-2.0-or-later
Group:          Productivity/Networking/File-Sharing
URL:            http://www.gnome.org/
# Disable Source URL, use git checkout via service
